---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import { Code } from "astro:components";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<div class="my-0 bg-cream px-0 py-8 sm:space-y-24 sm:px-8 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-8 sm:mx-32">
    <ContentSection title="Cue the Aladdin Soundtrack" id="intro">
      <Fragment slot="lead">
        <span class="text-center">
          Marketing Just Entered <br class="invisible sm:visible" /><span
            class="relative top-[-5px] italic text-orange sm:top-0"
            >A Whole New World</span
          >
        </span>
      </Fragment>
      <div class="m-auto text-darksteel">
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-0 text-left sm:gap-20">
          <div class="w-full flex-1 sm:w-2/3">
            <p>
              We’re living in unprecedented times: today the use of AI in
              business is rapidly expanding.
              <span class="font-bold">
                But when everyone else is turning to AI to grow their business,
                the way to stand out in this increasingly artificial world is to
                be relatably, authentically yourself.
              </span>
            </p>
            <br />
            <p class="font-bold text-orange">
              The competitive advantage you've been looking for is genuine
              human-to-human connection.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
              Marketing For Humans is the proven system for solopreneurs to <span
                class="font-bold"
                >learn how to grow your business, attract your ideal customers,
                and generate more revenue than you thought possible</span
              > — all through the power of marketing like a human.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex hidden flex-col items-center justify-center sm:block sm:w-1/3"
          >
            <img
              class="w-full max-w-96 rotate-3"
              src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/5f2ae813361eff3ad9282b29/63e69408eaf0942910cd57b8_B-School_iMac-p-800.png"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </ContentSection>
  </div>
</div>
